quicklab-pv - persistent volume configuration for loki on quicklab (don't use anywhere else)

ocp prom password:
	oc project openshift-monitoring
	secret: grafana-datasources: data: prometheus.yaml > base64 -d
			basicAuthPassword

logging sg with metrics:
	edit the logging sg template in STO and add metrics there

getting loki and qdr metrics to prometheus
	oc apply loki and qdr servicemonitors

deploy test-qdr

change test-qdr service to nodeport to expose the port (use that port + the worker ip in rsyslog)
